{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Flask/Flask-SQLAlchemy-ORM","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"240210c4-c34d-5982-8364-927b491e9795","html":"<h2 id=\"query\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#query\" aria-label=\"query permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>query</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>*로 전체 데이터를 가져오는 것 보다 id만 추출해서 가져오는게 훨씬 빠름</li>\n<li>단, limit가 걸려있을 땐 데이터의 개수가 정해져 있으므로 별 차이 안날수도 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># SQLAlchemy</span>\nquery <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>query<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>status <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 수정 전</span>\nquery <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> db<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>session<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>query<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(